Package: Radix_Sort
Type: Package
Title: Radix Sort Algorithm and Performance Evaluation
Version: 1.0
Date: 2025-03-28
Author: Loïc XU, Hajar LAMTAAI, Adèle BERGER
Maintainer: Loïc XU <loic.xu@example.com>, Hajar LAMTAAI <hajarlamtaai25@gmail.com>, Adèle BERGER <adele.berger18@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides implementations of the Radix Sort algorithm, and other sort algorithm in R and C++. It includes performance evaluations, complexity analysis, and comparisons with other sorting algorithms like Merge Sort, Heap Sort and Quick Sort. The package also supports the simulation of algorithmic complexity and the comparison of execution times between R and C++.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
